# Testing

## Framework

Vitest. Run with `pnpm test`.

## Required coverage

| Change type | Test requirement |
|-------------|------------------|
| New scan rule | Unit test with fixture strings; assert finding severity + recordIds |
| Adapter path logic | Snapshot or fixture tree under `packages/*/fixtures/` |
| WriteGuard | Test backup created, undo restores, sqlite write blocked by default |
| API route | `app.request()` integration test |

## Fixtures

- Use synthetic memory text — never copy real user rules or MEMORY.md
- Fixture dirs: `packages/adapter-cursor/fixtures/`, `packages/adapter-claude-code/fixtures/`
- Keep fixtures minimal (one concern per fixture)

## Assertions

- Prefer exact match on `ruleId` and `severity`
- Avoid testing implementation details; test observable outputs
